This issue has been addressed by implementing the two following classes (I would be glad to reference this in the issue you linked if it can provide any help) (credits to [maxc137](https://stackoverflow.com/users/4312132/maxc137?tab=profile) from this [stackoverflow post](https://stackoverflow.com/a/68914222/3021241))

